    <p>In March, I asked for a kerb-cut ramp to be built at Teck Whye Av­enue fronting Choa Chu Kang Poly­clinic to ben­e­fit peo­ple with dis­abil­i­ties and oth­ers.</p>
    <p>In May, the Land Trans­port Au­thor­ity agreed to carry out the works, which started on Mon­day.</p>
    <p>It took longer than usual, but I still want to thank staff at Traf­fic Scheme De­sign Devel­op­ment for their hard work to im­ple­ment this fea­ture.</p>
    <p>Loong Chik Tong</p>


